				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anaxagoras" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1019930); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1019930&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227545" alt="Anaxagoras" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1019930)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anaxagoras" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1019930); return false;" >Anaxagoras</a></span> <span class="odate time_1321285697 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">14 Nov 2011 15:48</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1305532">
									

<p>I really, really want to like this. But there are a few issues I really can't get over. First off, this seems far too malicious for a Factory item. Factory items are basically all useful, in a kind of warped way. They don't really have too much in the way of random arbitrary side effects.</p>
<p>Regarding the arbitrary side effects: I like the spam thing, but the thing with the viewers sexual proclivities growing more &quot;depraved&quot; just doesn't work. More deviant relative to what social norm? There have been a number of societies where pedophilia is commonplace or even required.</p>
<p>Sorry, this just doesn't quite work.</p>

